          h3 Detect Community Stucture In Social Networks
        div.modal-body
          div.projDesc
            h5
              span Language: Java
              span(style='float: right;') Duration: 07/2016 - 07/2016
            hr

            p Networks, especially Social Networks, often present Community Structure - 
              q a Network is said to have Community Structure if the nodes of the network can be grouped into sets of nodes such that each set of nodes is densely connected internally. 
              | - Wikipedia
            
            p In this project, I successfully implemented the following parts:
            ul
              li
                h5 Girvan-Newman Algorithm
                ul(style='list-style-type: circle;')
                  li Graph is Implemented as Ajacency List.
                  li Rotation-invariant Hashcode is Implemented for the Edge.
                  li Compute "betweenness" of Each Edge.
                  li Modularity Function is Implemented to Determine the Termination Condition.
                  li Terminate Splitting if Second Local Peaks of Modularity Appears or Max Iteration is Reached.
              
              li 
                h5 GML Parser
                ul(style='list-style-type: circle;')
                  li GML: Graph Modeling Language.

              li
                h5 Graph Visualization
                ul(style='list-style-type: circle;')
                  li Use Open Source Library - Graphstream to draw the Force-Directed Graph.

            hr

