            q The purpose of the algorithm is image retargeting, which is the problem of displaying images without distortion on media of various sizes using document standards, like HTML, that already support dynamic changes in page layout and text but not images

            p(style='float: right;') - Wikipedia

            p(style='clear: both;') In this project, I successfully implemented the following parts:
            ul
              li
                h5 Seam Carving Algorithm
                ul(style='list-style-type: circle;')
                  li Use java.awt.Color class to extract picture information.
                  li Implement Dual Gradient Energy Function to Computed Energy of Each Pixel.
                  li Reverse Post Order Traversal of a Graph
                  li Depth First Search to Find the Seam with Least Energy.

